	   <tr><td colspan=2>Whenever an item has the name of a god following the item's special properties (i.e. magic, no drop, no rent, lore.) then anyone wishing to wear the item must worship that god.  So a gnome cleric of brell is just as unable to use the item as a gnome SK of bertox.  <br>&nbsp;<br>Life's a bitch, and then you gotta beg for a rez.<br>   -Tellemar Shadowbane</td></tr>
